User:

- Add ability to amend user details


Exercise:

- Create different exercises
- Save exercises
- Add exercises to a specific workout


Workout:

- Choose workout from a list
- Add exercises to this workout (incl. sets, reps, rest times)


Progress Tracker:

- Track completed workouts, including sets and reps
- Include ability to generate reports with progress over time


Menu System:

- Interface which allows the user to navigate through the different options:
    * View Profile - Displays user info
    * Edit Profile - Updates user info
    * View Exercises - Allows user to choose a workout and displays the exercises (including latest additions / removals)
    * Track Progress - Log workouts and view progress reports
